# Plans for research {background="#000000"}

## Phase 1 (Months 1 - 3)

-   plan dissemination (blogs, publications, conferences, outreach, youtube)
-   review how researchers utilise AI in research; identify the area that would most benefit from a quality metric
-   identify grants/ opportunities to extend funding for KODAQ
-   design study for evaluation and review of KODAQ output and collect data (open ended feedback, survey data, web traffic)

## Phase 2 (Months 4 - 8)

-   co-creation workshops on output improvements
-   build MVP for one AI metric

## Phase 3 (Months 9 - 11)

-   output plans for next iteration
-   output AI metric
